      },
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2024R1) is subject to vendor-managed SQA including automated regression testing across 1,200+ benchmark cases. Internal audit confirmed version-controlled build artifacts and traceable release notes. Gradation 3 achieved: independent verification of regression suite completeness performed by FDA CDRH reviewer."
