      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/ac/use-error-mrl5",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Use error gradation 3 — independent review of simulation setup",
        "description": "An independent reviewer (not the simulation analyst) must verify mesh topology, boundary condition assignments, solver settings, and post-processing scripts before results are accepted. Achieved: independent review completed by second analyst; discrepancies resolved and documented."
      },
      "rationale": "An independent senior CFD analyst (not involved in model setup) conducted a structured review of all simulation inputs including mesh topology, boundary condition assignments, turbulence model settings (SST k-ω), hemolysis UDF parameters, and post-processing NIH integration scripts. Two minor discrepancies (inlet turbulence intensity specification and hemolysis integration volume) were identified and corrected prior to final simulation runs. Review record UR-2025-001 documents all findings and resolutions."
    },
    {
